{
    "version": 5,
    "bundle": "PBCTJCL6NQBRVU5TCWEKG7BS64SJ2HJZ",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "041071004",
    "title": "プリズム、出会い",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "それでは、改めまして……メジロアルダンと申します。\r\nこれからなにとぞ、よろしくお願いいたします。",
            "enText": "Well then, once more…… my name is Mejiro Ardan. \nFrom now on, I look forward to working under your kind guidance.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 284,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "よろしくな、アルダン",
                    "enText": "Looking forward to it, Ardan",
                    "nextBlock": 2
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "よろしくね、アルダン",
                    "enText": "Looking forward to it, Ardan",
                    "nextBlock": 2
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 188,
                    "pathId": 7434124463845125796
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": -4968581518446241740
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3864682753184327158,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "はいっ。\r\n……ではさっそく、というのもなんなのですが。",
            "enText": "Yes. \n…Well, this might seem a bit sudden, but―",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 184,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": 724148560058425585
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -7478174161280853435
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7285805223788370302,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "今週末、お付き合い願えますでしょうか？\r\n――トレーナーさん。",
            "enText": "This weekend, could I ask you to accompany me? \n-Trainer-san.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 180,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": 7284904161401045309
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 53,
                    "pathId": -2278094497636791543
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4875520680965897225,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "と、いうことで――",
            "enText": "And, just like that―",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 56,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 94,
                    "pathId": -2515046961834171354
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 29,
                    "pathId": -3368321404818765493
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 29,
                    "pathId": -1383392485870598213
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3154850762181805266,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ばあや",
            "enName": "Elderly Maid",
            "jpText": "では……アルダンお嬢様、お気をつけて行ってらっしゃいませ。\r\nトレーナー様、お嬢様のこと、なにとぞよろしくお願いいたします。",
            "enText": "Well then… my lady Ardan, be careful but please enjoy yourself. \nTrainer-sama, please take good care of my lady.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 392,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "は、はい！",
                    "enText": "Y-yes!",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 3434465472485515527
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 168,
                    "pathId": -8391704883014474406
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3100263518549908009,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……メジロ家の『お車』に乗せられて、\r\n美術館までやって来たのだった。",
            "enText": "…After riding in a vehicle provided by the Mejiro household, we arrived \nat an art gallery.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 5006557653278309092
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": 655500354880694150
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5905662851219065582,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "ふふっ、トレーナーさん、どうぞそう硬くならずに。\r\nばあや、お見送りありがとう。行って参りますね。",
            "enText": "Fufuu, Trainer-san, there's no need to be so stiff. \nGranny, thanks for escorting us. We'll be off then.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 326,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 230,
                    "pathId": 4553823664493943457
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 152,
                    "pathId": -8895286877415361492
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1886465315197431283,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "先ほどまでの緊張が残っているせいか、\r\nつい落ち着かない気分であたりを見回してしまう……。",
            "enText": "Maybe it was because I was still a little nervous from earlier, \nbut I couldn't keep calm and ended up glancing around…",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 103,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 115,
                    "pathId": 4215921424680640224
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 64,
                    "pathId": 3464412264921966625
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2402512108534016139,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "すると、現在行われていると思しき企画展のタイトルが目に入った。",
            "enText": "When I do, I happen to see what is apparently the title \nof this special exhibit.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "……『刹那展』？",
                    "enText": "…'Temporary Exposition'?",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 115,
                    "pathId": 3161798616044975891
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": 4853548245610565663
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 891541789248270949,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "はい。……もともと興味があり、足を運ぶつもりでいましたが、\r\nぜひトレーナーさんにもお付き合いいただきたいと思いまして。",
            "enText": "Yes…… originally I had planned to explore the exhibit myself \nsince I was interested, but I wanted to see if Trainer-san \nwould accompany me.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 347,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "どういう展示なんだ？",
                    "enText": "What kind of exhibition is it?",
                    "nextBlock": 11
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "どういう展示なの？",
                    "enText": "What kind of exhibition is it?",
                    "nextBlock": 11
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -9066151517975078901
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 103,
                    "pathId": -343252768282496930
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5227585031262238789,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "……種別は、多岐にわたります。\r\n絵画、彫刻、写真、映像、工芸――",
            "enText": "…There's a wide variety of exhibits. \nPainting, sculptures, photographs, film, handicrafts―",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 402,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 221,
                    "pathId": -2542583305493497190
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 51,
                    "pathId": 2458033867895083654
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2059710207907765174,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "しかしそれらは、ただ1つの共通項を持っています。",
            "enText": "But each and every one of those, has one single common theme.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 143,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "……共通項って？",
                    "enText": "…A theme?",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 155,
                    "pathId": 1819239006864591107
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 155,
                    "pathId": -869391260188573029
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2714280404386860679,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "全てが、『遺作』であるということです。",
            "enText": "All of these were completed 'posthumously'.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 131,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": 706277290997318483
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": -4465407780864684485
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6665706440717678105,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "場内には、確かに多種多様な作品が飾られていた。\r\n『すべてが遺作』と聞いていたので、最初はどこか構えていたが――",
            "enText": "In this venue, there certainly were a lot of works on display. \nAfter hearing these were all completed posthumously, at first I thought \nthis would be a somewhat formal affair, but―",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 118,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 34,
                    "pathId": 7005993459402177556
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7711232166627397317,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "実際に眺めて回ると、足が止まるものもあれば首を捻るばかりの\r\nものもある、言ってしまえば『普通』の美術展であった。",
            "enText": "When I actually looked around, there were things that made me \nstop and look, and things that made me contemplate, if I had to say it, \nit seemed like a normal art exhibition.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "pathId": 819664078921635420,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "そうですね。\r\n受け取り手にとっては、得てしてそういうものだと思います。",
            "enText": "That's true. To most people, I think that's often the way it seems.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 213,
            "pathId": -4878643237095429619,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ということで、場内をじっくりと見て回り、\r\n外へと戻って来たのだが――",
            "enText": "After that, we took our time looking around the venue. \nAnd when we stepped back outside―",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 145,
                    "pathId": 107189517463271249
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 146,
                    "pathId": 2590181065053878857
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7760595798011817053,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "トレーナーさん、あともう1か所だけ。\r\n美術館裏手の森へ、行ってもよろしいでしょうか？",
            "enText": "Trainer-san, there's one more place I'd like to stop by. \nThere's a forest behind the art gallery, would it be alright to take a look?",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 307,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 241,
                    "pathId": -6940650247480256430
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 173,
                    "pathId": -5393264443767875146
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 310435652155814366,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "実は、そこに最後の作品が展示されているのです。\r\n……どうしても、それだけは見ておきたくて。",
            "enText": "You see, there's one last work that's on display there. \n…No matter what, I'd really like to see it at least once.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 306,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": 4410190269813855606
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -8307624730667360596
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2992263365716466399,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "もう少しだけ、お付き合い願います。",
            "enText": "Could I trouble you to accompany me for just a bit longer?",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 125,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 107,
                    "pathId": 9156120162129735203
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 41,
                    "pathId": 2399369576317731782
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5388664848610166118,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "共に森へと足を運ぶ。そもそも作品があるということを\r\n知っている者が少ないのか、他の客は見当たらなかった。",
            "enText": "Together we headed in to the forest. It seemed like not many people \nknew about this work, since I didn't see any other visitors around.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 114,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": -5294537125238359372
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 6107524112513729853
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6945193864352202940,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "けれど、そこには――",
            "enText": "But, at the place―",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 58,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 33,
                    "pathId": 4044387919357819352
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 940861469115691636,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "ああ……そうです、これが。\r\n……これが、見たかったのです。",
            "enText": "Yes… that's right, this is it. \n…This is what I wanted to see.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 369,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 381,
                    "pathId": -644889734101351648
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": 11291140358371304
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2019994944215908617,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そこには、1枚の絵画が。",
            "enText": "There was a single painting.",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 60,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 85,
                    "pathId": 5319727771265121987
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": -7329734461994694147
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6612345408931098330,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……日に焼け、雨ざらしになり、見る影もなく色褪せた、\r\n1枚の絵画があった。",
            "enText": "…Sun bleached, weatherbeaten, faded until it was a shadow \nof its former self, a single painting.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": -7119063030768691606
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": -1225123103767959826
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5780301024040099793,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "作者の方は、この絵の展示を『外に限り』許す、\r\nと言い遺されたそうです。",
            "enText": "The one who created this, said this work could \"only be displayed outside\", \nas part of their will it seems.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 276,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 229,
                    "pathId": 1956899520764174515
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": -6252806733355140019
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1584024606069488865,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "…………………………。",
            "enText": "………………",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 53,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 68,
                    "pathId": 3678449578958427341
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 24,
                    "pathId": 3740998210209289834
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6455009114653169720,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "長い、長い時間を、メジロアルダンと共に\r\n黙って絵を見つめながら過ごした――",
            "enText": "For a long, long time, together with Mejiro Ardan, \nI stayed silently gazing at the picture―",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": 7297645289980786880
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3574811499575986838,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "もう、ご存じのこととは思いますが。\r\n……私は生まれつき、あまりに弱く、脆い体をしております。",
            "enText": "As I'm sure you're already aware. \n…I was born with a frail, extremely weak body.",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 355,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "……ああ",
                    "enText": "……Yeah",
                    "nextBlock": 30
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "……うん",
                    "enText": "……Yeah",
                    "nextBlock": 30
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 241,
                    "pathId": -1795502205311020082
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 17,
                    "pathId": -4331397810431636456
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3226873727534204773,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "美術館を離れ、カフェでひと息ついた時のこと。\r\nメジロアルダンは、静かにそう語り始めた。",
            "enText": "After leaving the art gallery, we were taking a short break at a cafe. \nThat was how Mejiro Ardan, calmly started our conversation.",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 102,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": 3667876360082048097
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 9142924069493810179,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "それでも、同じく脆いと言われた脚を持って生まれた姉は\r\n奇跡的に回復したからと、一縷の望みをかけましたが――",
            "enText": "Even so, my older sister, who was also born with a weak constitution, \nmiraculously recovered, and I've been holding on to that faint \nsliver of hope, but―",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 318,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 330,
                    "pathId": 8253924748660136864
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 28,
                    "pathId": 3874880852478473032
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5657941524066797902,
            "blockIdx": 31
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "どうやら、そう甘くはありませんでした。世の常、ですね。",
            "enText": "It seems that, things haven't been going that smoothly. \nBut that's how it normally is, isn't it?",
            "nextBlock": 33,
            "origClipLength": 262,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": -9059837865087152296
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 17,
                    "pathId": 1127264103012772831
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4019344597659846216,
            "blockIdx": 32
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "主治医からは『率直に言ってレースに耐えうる体ではない』\r\n『ケガや故障と隣り合わせになるだろう』と診断されました。",
            "enText": "My physician told me \"To put it blunty, your body is not built for racing. \nInjuries and worse could be waiting for you based on my examinations.\"",
            "nextBlock": 34,
            "origClipLength": 373,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 411,
                    "pathId": -2861576979718263466
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 196,
                    "pathId": 674509066742178713
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2229109370809643346,
            "blockIdx": 33
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "……両親は、いまだに私が競走生活を送ることに反対しています。\r\n私を失うことが恐ろしくて堪らないと、先日も電話で泣かれました。",
            "enText": "…My parents, even now, are against me racing. While in tears, \nthey told me they were dreadfully afraid of what might happen to me \njust the other day.",
