        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "私は本来双子で生まれる予定でしたが――片方は死産でしたので。\r\n同じ結末に至らせるわけにはいかないと、必死なのでしょう。",
            "enText": "I was originally supposed to be born with a twin but… the other was \nstillborn. They're probably desperate to make sure I don't \nmeet a similar end.",
